<p>Save the resulting panorama into the 03-photomerge &gt; 00-photos-to-merge folder.</p>

<h3 id="contact-sheet">Contact Sheet</h3>

<p>Create a contact sheet with the provided photos. Save the file(s) in the 04-contact-sheet folder.</p>
